  "text": "The HOS is a self-report questionnaire composed of 28 questions divided into two subscales: Activities of Daily Living (ADLs; 19 items) and Sports (nine items) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The total score of each subscale ranges from 0 to 100, where higher scores denote better hip function. The scores for each subscale were calculated separately [CITATION_3] .",
